description: Returns runtime data for each step in a runtime instance of the workflow that you specify in the request.

parameters.name: workflowExecutionId
parameters.description: The unique identifier that Image Builder assigned to keep track of runtime details when it ran the workflow.

nested_items.name: requestId
nested_items.description: The request ID that uniquely identifies this request.

nested_items.name: steps
nested_items.description: Contains an array of runtime details that represents each step in this runtime instance of the workflow.

nested_items.name: stepExecutionId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for the workflow step, assigned at runtime.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the workflow step.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: Runtime status for the workflow step.

nested_items.name: rollbackStatus
nested_items.description: Reports on the rollback status of the step, if applicable.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: Detailed output message that the workflow step provides at runtime.

nested_items.name: inputs
nested_items.description: Input parameters that Image Builder provides for the workflow step.

nested_items.name: outputs
nested_items.description: The file names that the workflow step created as output for this runtime instance of the workflow.

nested_items.name: startTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the workflow step started.

nested_items.name: endTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the workflow step finished.

nested_items.name: workflowBuildVersionArn
nested_items.description: The build version ARN for the Image Builder workflow resource that defines the steps for this runtime instance of the workflow.

nested_items.name: workflowExecutionId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier that Image Builder assigned to keep track of runtime details when it ran the workflow.

nested_items.name: imageBuildVersionArn
nested_items.description: The image build version resource ARN that's associated with the specified runtime instance of the workflow.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: The output message from the list action, if applicable.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The next token used for paginated responses. When this field isn't empty, there are additional elements that the service hasn't included in this request. Use this token with the next request to retrieve additional objects.
